com.bmc.arsys.api

Class RecursiveComplexQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.api.ComplexQueryBase
      • com.bmc.arsys.api.RecursiveComplexQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQuerySource, Query, Cloneable

    public class RecursiveComplexQuery
extends ComplexQueryBase
implements IQuerySource, Cloneable
    The RecursiveQuery class is used to define the properties of a sub- or hierarchical query that works with complex operands that include functions, arithmetic operations and aggregates
    See Also:
    ComplexQueryBase, IQuerySource, QuerySourceForm
